{"id": 1209, "genre": 1000, "title": "这些“大叔级”营销都糟蹋了什么东西？", "description": "本来挺喜欢的，硬套上一大堆“传统”“陈酿”“品味人生”“大气典藏”乱七八糟的东西，我就不爱买了。（题图来自：Jeff Östberg）", "record_count": 10940, "comment_count": 31, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201609081340558NDnVT05MYxZB4QX.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-09-08T17:00:28Z", "questions": [{"id": 1094, "title": "这些“大叔级”营销都糟蹋了什么东西？", "content": "这些“大叔级”营销都糟蹋了什么东西？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 114010, "content": "爱喝茶，但很烦“茶道”、“禅意”的捆绑销售", "image": "img/option/option/20160907183202k9nx0PUB6mbGRTVe.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 114011, "content": "红酒总要扯上什么“慢工出精品，年久存香醇”", "image": "img/option/option/2016090718321249pbx6SMHgKUQeGh.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 114012, "content": "提起保险，总是绕不开“中老年必备”", "image": "img/option/option/20160907183327AfWSJNC5rGlcdEIZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 114013, "content": "老牌点心很好吃但总和传统文化扯上关系", "image": "img/option/option/20160907183430mA9YPVijRgQG4Mt5.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 114014, "content": "餐厅叫“XX大酒楼”、中秋还要发“XX酒楼月饼”", "image": "img/option/option/20160907183238uKPs9jioMDNERZJw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 114015, "content": "很想买羊绒衫，海报上全是叔叔阿姨在微笑", "image": "img/option/option/20160907183556gNF4tD12ipnde3vY.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 114016, "content": "套餐加上“商务”这两字就透着一股老气", "image": "img/option/option/20160907183630BxzspghHlUS8Z5JF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}